### 1. BASIC AI TEST
POST http://localhost:3000/generate-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is an RFP?"
}

---

### 1b. STRUCTURE RFP REQUIREMENTS (numbered list JSON)
POST http://localhost:3000/structure-rfp-requirements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "8. References: How many references (3 minimum)? 9. Demonstration: Will you require a demo? 10. Format: Submit in Word."
}

---

### 2. CONTEXT AI TEST (no file)
POST http://localhost:3000/ask-with-context
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is this document about?",
  "document": "This is an RFP for building a procurement system in 6 months with cloud infrastructure."
}

---

### 2b. EXTRACT IMPORTANT DATES (RFP text)
POST http://localhost:3000/extract-dates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "Sealed proposals must be received by March 15, 2026 at 2:00 PM local time. A pre-bid conference will be held on 03/01/2026. Bids will be opened publicly on March 16, 2026. Contract performance begins April 1, 2026 and ends September 30, 2027."
}

---

### 3. FILE UPLOAD AI TEST (IMPORTANT)
POST http://localhost:3000/ask-with-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

file: @sample.txt
question: What is this document about?

